properties.Description: The properties associated with the identity.

location.Description: The geo-location where the resource lives

tenantId.Description: The id of the tenant which the identity belongs to.

principalId.Description: The id of the service principal object associated with the created identity.

clientId.Description: The id of the app associated with the identity. This is a random generated UUID by MSI.

totalCount.Description: Total number of Azure resources assigned to the identity.

value.Description: The collection of Azure resources returned by the resource action to get a list of assigned resources.

nextLink.Description: The url to get the next page of results, if any.

resourceGroup.Description: The name of the resource group this resource belongs to.

subscriptionId.Description: The ID of the subscription this resource belongs to.

subscriptionDisplayName.Description: The name of the subscription this resource belongs to.
